Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:33.20,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,晚饭一会儿一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:34.42,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,舅舅也还没吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:41.30,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,舅舅…您难道不是她的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:44.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我家没有爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.50,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,噢 咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.15,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还有素炸的土豆和茄子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:53.57,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,名厨之作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.85,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还尝试加了些咖啡和酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.57,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,奇怪的隐藏佐料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:04.70,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,咦？
